Description: Join Andrea Griffiths, Senior Developer Advocate at GitHub, as she sits down with Jeff Cobble, Director of Cloud Platform Enablement at Fidelity Investments, at GitHub Universe 2025. They discuss how artificial intelligence is revolutionizing the software development lifecycle in enterprise environments, the critical importance of automation, and effective leadership strategies drawn from military experience. Jeff shares insights on enabling high-performing teams, addressing common misconceptions about enterprise tech, and maintaining fundamental engineering skills while leveraging advanced AI tools.
Author: GitHub
Title: A Marine's Playbook for Building High-Performance Developer Teams at Fidelity
